{
  "id": "adv_bond_chs_01_02",
  "title": "白石千紗2",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "羊毛フェルトかなぁ……刺繍もいいけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe wool felt… Embroidery is also good…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5366.666666700001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "お裁縫の本が、いっぱい……\n千紗ちゃん、何か作るの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are so many‚ sewing books…\nChisa-chan‚ are you making something…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "うん、ただ何を作ろうか悩んじゃってるんだけどね\nせっかくなら、みんなで使えるものがいいんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I'm just trying to decide what to make\nPreferably‚ it would be better if everyone could use it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.1999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "みんなで使えるもの……\nカーテンとか……部屋を仕切る、のれんとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone could use it…\nCurtains… room dividers‚ noren curtains…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.6333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、のれんって聞くと\nお店屋さんが思い浮かんじゃうけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ when I hear the noren curtains\nI think of the store side…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.0333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "リビングとか、キッチンで使うものは良さそうだね\n頑張って作ってみようかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It would be good to use in the living or kitchen\nLet's work hard to make it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.4333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗先生の新作、楽しみ……\n作ってくれたエコバッグ、毎日使ってるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ms. Chisa's new work‚ looking forward to it…\nEco bag you made for me‚ I use it every day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.3666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "せ、先生ってほどじゃないよ～\nでも、期待してくれてる分も頑張らなきゃ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I wouldn't go that far~\nBut‚ I have to work hard to live up to the expectations…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.9999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.2333339692,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hungry-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1100.0007629000024
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "（お腹空いた……）\n（夜ご飯まで時間あるし、何か食べようかな……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Hungry…）\n（It's still a long way until dinner‚ should I eat something…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.1333347321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "（……！）\n（テーブルの上に、美味しそうなバナナとリンゴが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…!）\n（On the table‚ bananas and apples look appetizing…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.9333347321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "（食べたい……）\n（今度買ってくるから……一本だけ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I want to eat…）\n（I'll buy one next time… just one…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.1000013988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "……？　取れない……\n……？　…………？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…? I can't pick it up…\n…? …?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.3000013988,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5866.66526789999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、雫ちゃん、気づいてくれた？\nそのテーブルクロス、私が作ったんだ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Shizuku-chan‚ did you notice?\nThat tablecloth‚ I made it~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.7999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "そのバナナの刺繍\nうまく出来たと思うんだけど、どうかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That banana embroidery‚\nI think it turned out well‚ what do you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.1333321889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "え……これ刺繍……！？　だまし絵みたい……\nじゃあ、こっちのリンゴは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… is this embroidery…?! It looks like an optical illusion art…\nWell‚ this apple is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.4333321889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "それは羊毛フェルトだよ\nそれも、ちょっとだけ気合い入れて作ってみたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's wool felt\nI made it‚ with a little bit of psyched up",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.8333321889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "……！？　本物かと思った……\n気合いが入り過ぎて、凄いことになってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…!? I thought it was real thing…\nYou're so psyched up‚ it's became a great thing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.6333321889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに褒められると照れちゃうよ～\nえへへ、でもうまく出来て、少し自信がついたかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel embarrassed when you praise me like that~\nEhehe‚ but it worked out well‚ so I think I gained some confidence",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.1666655223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "次は、みんなのマスコットを作ってみようと思うんだ～\nカバンとかにつけたら可愛いかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Next time‚ I'm thinking about making a mascot for everyone~\nIt would be cute to attach it to a bag or something",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.8666655223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_02-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "マスコットを作るなら、デフォルメした方がいいかも\nリアル過ぎるのがついてたら、びっくりしちゃうから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you're making a mascot‚ it might be better to stylized art style it\nIf there is too much realism‚ it will be surprising",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.4999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}